{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:45:07.947522+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 439672d72a3ae56a51725fc19de5cbf4e12f69f8)", "id": "lc_6b334382-6da2-4f8f-a157-a00da37f6007"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# Product Documentation Portal\n\nA Docusaurus documentation portal for product setup guides, installation notes, and maintenance documentation.\n\n## Project layout\n\n- `docs/` — Documentation pages rendered by Docusaurus.\n- `docusaurus.config.js` — Site configuration.\n- `sidebars.js` — Sidebar navigation.\n- `package.json` — Node scripts and dependencies.\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\nmake validate\n```\n```bash\nnpm install\n```\n```bash\nnpm run build\n```\n\n## Documentation workflow\n\n1. Add or update Markdown pages under `docs/`.\n2. Keep `sidebars.js` synchronized with new pages.\n3. Validate JavaScript config before opening a PR.\n4. Run a full Docusaurus build before release.\n\n## Maintenance notes\n\nUse the sidebar configuration when adding or moving documentation pages.\n\n## Contributing\n\nKeep changes focused, update documentation when behavior changes, and run the validation commands before submitting a pull request.\n", "id": "lc_ef6d3e65-948d-4773-82b2-3aac53aa3c0c"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "311ead31-5a3a-4db0-8d38-41f0b22b5ee1", "tool_call_id": "call_aa00991693624f00bf01af0c", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:45:14.679393+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've completed my investigation of Issue #1. Here's my analysis and the exact fix needed:\n\n## Issue #1 Analysis: Fix a broken documentation link\n\n### Root Cause\nIn `docs/intro.md`, the link to the Getting Started page uses a file extension `.md` which is broken in Docusaurus:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\nIn Docusaurus, links between documentation pages should use route-based paths (without the `.md` extension).\n\n### Current content of `docs/intro.md`:\n```markdown\n---\nid: intro\ntitle: Introduction\n---\n\n# Introduction\n\nThis is a clean Docusaurus benchmark repository.\n\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\n### Required Fix\nChange the link from `./getting-started.md` to `./getting-started`:\n\n```markdown\n---\nid: intro\ntitle: Introduction\n---\n\n# Introduction\n\nThis is a clean Docusaurus benchmark repository.\n\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started).\n```\n\n### Why this is a broken link\nThe `docusaurus.config.js` has `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'` configured, meaning any broken links will cause build failures. The correct Docusaurus linking convention uses route paths without file extensions.\n\n### Limitation\nUnfortunately, I'm unable to push this change to the repository due to permission restrictions (403 errors from the GitHub API). The repository appears to have restricted write access for the current authentication token.\n\nTo implement this fix, someone with write access needs to:\n1. Edit `docs/intro.md`\n2. Change `./getting-started.md` to `./getting-started` on line 11\n3. Run `make validate` to verify the change passes validation\n4. Run `npm run build` to verify no broken link errors occur", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 497, "prompt_tokens": 9907, "total_tokens": 10404, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 109, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 9600, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00020902, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 6.986e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00013916}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780875908-cx3orgC2vhrzSc5hrN3P", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea479-d36c-7663-b5d8-9f9a432499d8-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9907, "output_tokens": 497, "total_tokens": 10404, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 9600}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 109}}}}]}}}
